個垃圾po<br />\n獨立思考喇<br />\n連登仔<br />\n<br />\n推呢個喇<br />\n咪L推錯<br />\n<br />\n[再次置頂］614就大三罷公投，希望大家可以將依個po長期置頂<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2060320\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2060320</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區</span></span></span></span>"},{"pid":"0a48761cf3e425a7e055d7b1de2f6da46159a9fb","tid":2060530,"uid":167928,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-11T17:14:51.000Z","msg":"老豆未搵到仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RDqXMez.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRDqXMez.png&h=aec07c92&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6fe397d9b79e9706762c2c58d9583e29cc517f36","tid":2060530,"uid":241171,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-11T17:15:48.000Z","msg":"呢個官真係仆街到痴線 斷骨就當係事 咬到就襲警"},{"pid":"fd4a4eb22aab493785d7e63d1facc7b786e9ed6a","tid":2060530,"uid":26770,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-11T17:16:21.000Z","msg":"觀塘莫子聰裁判官<br />\n打到人斷肋骨就合理, 打人時遭受害人自然反應咬傷就砌嚴重傷人<br />\n<br />\n莫子聰同杜浩成係老死,同一庭的"},{"pid":"0da9afe432a9db47fe3f4c95a9b809b4fcf5f364","tid":2060530,"uid":285118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4f90000a839c4828e86d8ef365560fc23a0c1c22","tid":2060530,"uid":26770,"like":35,"dislike":1,"score":34,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-06-11T17:11:46.000Z","msg":"莫官又指，被告肋骨的裂傷相信是她和警員拉扯間失平衡、導致雙雙跌倒時造成，<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n真係正仆街<br />\n警犬打到示威者斷肋骨就意外<br />\n有牙印就示威者嚴重傷人"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-11T17:16:55.000Z","msg":"屌⋯⋯"},{"pid":"7a49d7b8a108bcf3e4df0813a746df8dd284d084","tid":2060530,"uid":37869,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"quote":{"pid":"4f90000a839c4828e86d8ef365560fc23a0c1c22","tid":2060530,"uid":26770,"like":35,"dislike":1,"score":34,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-06-11T17:11:46.000Z","msg":"莫官又指，被告肋骨的裂傷相信是她和警員拉扯間失平衡、導致雙雙跌倒時造成，<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n真係正仆街<br />\n警犬打到示威者斷肋骨就意外<br />\n有牙印就示威者嚴重傷人"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-11T17:17:37